title: [Ta'Vaalor, Victory Court]
[Ta'Vaalor, Tyrnian Court]
[Ta'Vaalor, King's Court]
description: Thick grey stone walls clad a large structure that dominates this part of the court.  Red and gold House Vaalor pennants flutter atop the crenelated walls, adding the only bit of color the building possesses.  A plain faenor sign is posted beside the entrance to the imposing hall.
